description:
Season Seven Match
TRINA MICHAELS
Passion
HT: 5'6
WT: 150 lbs
Season record (0-0)
Lifetime record (1-4)
JESSE COX
The Cheerleader
HT: 5'2
WT: 118lbs
Season record (0-1)
Lifetime record (0-1)
Trina Michaels is back and lets face it, this big titted, booming blond is horrible. Her only win was against Harmony, who is the worst of the worst. However, Trina has something on the mat that not many have: HUGE booming tits! Dude, look at the tits!
Jesse is a hot little blond living in CA. She did gymnastics and cheerleading in college, and she is still very active. She is fit, strong and determined to do well at US. In her first match she was destroyed by the Dragon. Did she learn enough to be able to beat one of the worst wrestlers in the history of US?
The Membership has been very vocal about seeing match ups with rookies vs. wrestlers they might be able to beat. We listened, we complied! This match was the closest match we have ever filmed! You cannot get the score closer then this was!
title: Trina "Passion" Michaels (0-0) vs Jesse "The Cheerleader" Cox (0-0)
